OmniDataTransform.description: This DR is used to fetch all the Profile Attributes.
OmniDataTransform.name: VPLGetAccountProfileAttributes

omniDataTransformItem.formulaExpression: COUNTQUERY ( "SELECT count() FROM vlocity_cmt__AttributeAssignment__c WHERE vlocity_cmt__ObjectId__c = '{0}' AND vlocity_cmt__IsActive__c = true AND vlocity_cmt__RemovedFlag__c = false AND vlocity_cmt__CategoryCode__c IN ('PURCHASE_CRITERIA_COST','PURCHASE_CRITERIA_RENEWABLE_ENERGY','PURCHASE_CRITERIA_FAMILY_FRIENDLY','PURCHASE_CRITERIA_SERVICE_AVAILABILITY','PURCHASE_CRITERIA_INSURANCE','CUSTOMER_SATISFACTION_COST','CUSTOMER_SATISFACTION_RELIABILITY','CUSTOMER_SATISFACTION_COVERAGE','CUSTOMER_SATISFACTION_SERVICE','CUSTOMER_SATISFACTION_MAINTENANCE','CUSTOMER_SATISFACTION_USAGE_CHARGES','ANALYSIS_MOOD','ANALYSIS_UPSELL_POTENTIAL','ANALYSIS_RENEWAL_POTENTIAL')",Account:Id)
omniDataTransformItem.name: VPLGetAccountProfileAttributes
